Abstract is a keyword.
Abstract class having abstract methods and concrete(implementation) methods.
If any class having one abstract method that class should be declared as a abstract otherwise that class will be showing compile time error.
If any class extends abstract class that class should be override all abstract methods otherwise the class will be showing compile time error.
We cannot create object to abstract class, but we can create reference to it.
Abstract class constructor will be called automatically during object class creation.
Abstract class constructor can be created but it will be called when we create sub class object. 